130
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:02,519
But I need a way to find you.

131
00:07:02,519 --> 00:07:04,000
You ought to give me a limit.

132
00:07:04,399 --> 00:07:05,959
I have no human heart,

133
00:07:06,399 --> 00:07:09,759
but the rules that govern people
apply to me too.

134
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:12,399
All right. I accept.

135
00:07:12,759 --> 00:07:14,000
Three months.

136
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:15,439
I'll find you

137
00:07:15,639 --> 00:07:17,399
and make you disappear for good.

138
00:07:17,519 --> 00:07:18,680
Why are you dozing off here?

139
00:07:24,759 --> 00:07:25,600
What's on your mind?

140
00:07:33,839 --> 00:07:35,759
I asked Assistant He
to get me some wine.

141
00:07:36,439 --> 00:07:38,040
