while you're standing in the cold.

142
00:07:52,199 --> 00:07:53,000
Dongfang Yan,

143
00:07:54,399 --> 00:07:56,079
do you think

144
00:07:56,079 --> 00:07:57,959
I'll always win?

145
00:08:04,279 --> 00:08:05,480
You've never lost.

146
00:08:11,519 --> 00:08:12,560
Ms. Xi…

147
00:08:19,850 --> 00:08:24,425
